WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.056
One number tells us how wrong a

00:00:02.056 --> 00:00:02.644
guess is.

00:00:02.644 --> 00:00:04.112
We call it the loss.

00:00:04.112 --> 00:00:05.875
Smaller loss means a better guess.

00:00:05.875 --> 00:00:07.931
So, loss is one number that tells

00:00:07.931 --> 00:00:09.400
us how wrong we are.
